headline: Why Constellation Brands (STZ) Shares Are Trading Lower Today
summary: Shares of beer, wine, and spirits company Constellation Brands (NYSE:STZ) fell 3.3% in the afternoon session after RBC Capital trimmed its price target on the stock to $230 from $233, though it maintained an Outperform rating.
